snippet.title: Science Kombat: Super Interessante (Full Walkthrough)
snippet.description:
Science Kombat is a free-to-play browser-based game that let's some of history’s most famous scientists duke it out in an epic grudge match. You can choose from Einstein, Tesla, Pythagoras, Hawking, Turing, Darwin, Newton and Curie, and each comes with their own set of science-based power-ups.

Play The Game: http://especiais.super.abril.com.br/science-kombat/index.html

Don't Forget To Like & Subscribe For More...
